---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
export async function getStaticPaths() {
  return [
    { params: { slug: 'airbnb-buys-manhattan-office' } },
    { params: { slug: 'dallas-miami-financial-hub' } },
  ];
}
const { slug } = Astro.params;
---

<PageLayout title="Brief">
  <article class="article-page section-padding">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: var(--container-narrow);">
      <div class="article-meta">
        <span class="article-category">Office</span>
        <time>July 10, 2026</time>
      </div>
      <h1 class="article-title">Airbnb Buys Manhattan Office Despite NYC Rental Crackdown</h1>
      <div class="article-share">
        <span>Share:</span>
        <a href="#" aria-label="Copy link">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M4 10a2 2 0 1 1 0-4 2 2 0 0 1 0 4zM12 6a2 2 0 1 1 0-4 2 2 0 0 1 0 4zM12 14a2 2 0 1 1 0-4 2 2 0 0 1 0 4z"/><path d="M6.5 9.5l3 1M9.5 5.5l-3 1"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="article-hero-image">
        <div class="article-hero-placeholder"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="article-body">
        <p>Airbnb's $81.5M acquisition of a landmark NYC office signals a long-term presence in a city with strict short-term rental laws. The company purchased a 12-story building in Manhattan's Flatiron District, marking one of the largest office acquisitions by a tech company in the city this year.</p>
        <p>The move comes despite ongoing regulatory challenges facing short-term rentals in New York City, where strict registration requirements and occupancy limits have significantly reduced the available inventory.</p>
        <p>"This investment demonstrates our commitment to New York and our confidence in the future of the city," said an Airbnb spokesperson.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</PageLayout>

<style>
  .article-page { padding-top: calc(var(--header-height) + 2rem); }
  .article-meta { display: flex; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .article-category { font-size: 0.8125rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-accent); }
  .article-meta time { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); }
  .article-title { font-size: var(--fs-heading-1); line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .article-share { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .article-share span { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); }
  .article-share a { color: var(--color-text-muted); transition: color var(--transition-fast); }
  .article-share a:hover { color: var(--color-accent); }
  .article-hero-placeholder {
    width: 100%;
    padding-bottom: 52%;
    background: var(--color-bg-subtle);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .article-body p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-body);
  }
</style>
